LIST YOUR OFFER
Add a campaign summary: audience interest, age, gender, country and even ethnicity. Send brief to have qualified creators opt in.


CREATORS SUBMIT CONTENT
Selected creators follow your brief and submit their produced branded content via their Insense mobile App.


APPROVE CREATOR’S CONTENT
Chat with multiple creators directly and accept/reject submitted content.


WATCH YOUR CONTENT GO LIVE
...And reach your target audiences with unique creator content


TRACK CAMPAIGN RESULTS
...within your dash. Select best content for re-amplification across paid & owned channels






BUILD A CAMPAIGN
Add a campaign summary, budget, quickly select the most relevant influencers or send a bid.






INFLUENCERS PRODUCE CONTENT
Influencers accept or deny their participation in our App and start producing content for your brand.






CHOOSE BRANDED CONTENT
You can review unique branded content produced by multiple influencers via your dashboard and communicate with them directly.






GET REACH
Once you approve content for posting, you start reaching thousands of followers. You can review the stats for each campaign in your Dashboard.






CONVERT REACH TO ACTIONS
WOW! Run official Ad Campaigns on Instagram and Facebook via your dashboard.
Reach an already engaged audience multiple times and convert it to installs or sign-ups with 2x times lower CPA!











