We're market leaders.
ADS invests heavily in training, providing 80 hours of formal training per new employee annually. We offer the uncommon opportunity to work as a team in a dynamically growing organization that plays a vital role in supporting over 4,000 defense customers worldwide.










We hire from within.
We are committed to hiring and training ADS team members from within the military community. More than one third of ADS employees are veterans or members of military families which is why we have been awarded the distinction of Military Friendly Employer.










One Team.
One Fight.
ADS is proud to be an equal opportunity employer. We support a diverse and inclusive workforce where all team members are treated fairly and given equal opportunity to perform to their fullest potential.










  





